We rescued him from the Earth Fiends.

332
00:22:19,527 --> 00:22:20,688
But he wasn't lucky enough

333
00:22:21,608 --> 00:22:22,928
to undergo the natural fire.

334
00:22:23,128 --> 00:22:24,608
