335
00:22:26,087 --> 00:22:27,567
The Whip Clan excels at taming.

336
00:22:28,567 --> 00:22:29,567
Perfect timing.

337
00:22:30,727 --> 00:22:32,168
Let's see if you have any idea.

338
00:22:36,007 --> 00:22:36,968
I have plenty way

339
00:22:37,087 --> 00:22:37,928
