380
00:25:11,888 --> 00:25:13,047
Good choice.

381
00:25:13,188 --> 00:25:13,688
Let's go.

382
00:25:13,688 --> 00:25:15,208
Wait, what's wrong?

383
00:25:15,247 --> 00:25:16,408
Take care.

384
00:25:17,208 --> 00:25:18,047
Don't look back.

385
00:25:18,368 --> 00:25:19,168
Watch your step.

386
00:25:20,527 --> 00:25:21,327
Wait, we...

387
00:25:21,327 --> 00:25:22,688
No questions. Follow me.

388
