393
00:26:15,767 --> 00:26:16,487
I'm sorry.

394
00:26:16,888 --> 00:26:17,408
I was

395
00:26:17,408 --> 00:26:19,087
too focused on checking on you

396
00:26:19,128 --> 00:26:20,087
