00:27:58,087 --> 00:27:59,448
Herbal beef filling.

421
00:27:59,608 --> 00:28:00,567
New filling.

422
00:28:01,327 --> 00:28:02,807
Fill your stomach

423
00:28:03,007 --> 00:28:04,327
