430
00:28:14,807 --> 00:28:15,408
Stop.

431
00:28:17,007 --> 00:28:18,287
You don't need nourishment.

432
00:28:18,688 --> 00:28:19,368
Too much for you.

433
00:28:23,247 --> 00:28:24,087
It's delicious.

434
00:28:26,888 --> 00:28:28,047
I've never seen someone cook

435
00:28:28,047 --> 00:28:29,567
