442
00:28:40,767 --> 00:28:42,408
You can eat them whenever you want.

443
00:28:43,968 --> 00:28:44,567
Mr. Changxi.

444
00:28:44,648 --> 00:28:47,007
You should have Ms. Lu
teach you to cook other dishes.

445
00:28:47,007 --> 00:28:48,527
Sharing knowledge.

