449
00:28:56,648 --> 00:28:57,448
Is that okay?

450
00:28:57,608 --> 00:28:58,727
Got it. I'll make it done.

451
00:29:00,128 --> 00:29:01,727
Thank you, Mr. Yan.

452
00:29:02,567 --> 00:29:03,208
Eat up.

453
00:29:04,128 --> 00:29:04,727
Wait.

454
00:29:04,928 --> 00:29:06,527
Here, Mr. Yan. Have one.

455
00:29:09,527 --> 00:29:11,128
