477
00:30:24,208 --> 00:30:26,848
Mr. Changxi spent half his life
mastering his craft.

478
00:30:26,928 --> 00:30:28,487
He teaches Ms. Lu the filling,

479
00:30:29,087 --> 00:30:30,527
and teaches you the wrapping.

480
00:30:30,807 --> 00:30:33,168
You can inherit the Changxi Dumplings.

481
