503
00:31:59,128 --> 00:32:00,007
Mr. Gou Ya.

504
00:32:01,688 --> 00:32:03,767
Omnivorous? A nice way to put it.

505
00:32:03,968 --> 00:32:04,727
Actually, it's...

506
00:32:04,727 --> 00:32:05,327
Eating humans.

507
00:32:08,408 --> 00:32:09,567
So this means

508
00:32:12,128 --> 00:32:14,767
