won't make them more human-like,

509
00:32:15,208 --> 00:32:16,807
but actually reveals their true nature.

510
00:32:18,888 --> 00:32:19,807
Exactly.

511
00:32:27,888 --> 00:32:29,047
This is a primal Earth Fiend.

512
00:32:30,087 --> 00:32:31,128
To become human,

513
00:32:31,487 --> 00:32:32,448
