531
00:33:36,448 --> 00:33:37,287
Roommate?

532
00:33:39,968 --> 00:33:40,727
For safety,

533
00:33:40,727 --> 00:33:42,727
they should live alone.

534
00:33:43,408 --> 00:33:44,928
They live with someone,

535
00:33:44,928 --> 00:33:46,208
