541
00:34:03,287 --> 00:34:05,047
Who does Lin Xirou live with?

542
00:34:06,007 --> 00:34:06,688
Me

543
00:34:07,527 --> 00:34:08,328
and Lin Ling.

544
00:34:12,448 --> 00:34:13,207
Tell me.

545
00:34:14,288 --> 00:34:15,607
Did you run away from home

546
00:34:15,607 --> 00:34:17,007
or attempt to kill yourself?

547
00:34:18,728 --> 00:34:19,607
What?

548
00:34:19,928 --> 00:34:21,848
They say quiet people
harbor wild streaks.

549
00:34:22,167 --> 00:34:24,368
You must've done something shocking

550
00:34:25,127 --> 00:34:26,248
