I'm older than Lin Ling,

573
00:35:35,888 --> 00:35:37,207
so I should be first in line.

574
00:35:37,968 --> 00:35:39,047
But she never urged me,

575
00:35:39,047 --> 00:35:39,848
only Lin Ling.

576
00:35:43,288 --> 00:35:44,928
Descendants?

577
00:35:45,288 --> 00:35:47,007
You're only mentioning this now?

578
00:35:47,448 --> 00:35:48,448
I don't care.

579
00:35:48,567 --> 00:35:49,647
Slaughter a cow right now,

580
00:35:49,647 --> 00:35:51,408
and get me my 40 jin of meat.

581
00:35:51,696 --> 00:35:53,866
If I have no meat,
I couldn't open the shop tomorrow.

582
00:35:54,087 --> 00:35:55,448
Keep your words.

583
00:35:55,687 --> 00:35:56,968
Or you'll ruin the bond I had

584
00:35:56,968 --> 00:35:57,687
with your dad.

585
00:35:58,207 --> 00:36:00,127
Huzi, let me tell you the truth.

586
00:36:00,527 --> 00:36:02,328
Your dad ruined things with drinking.

587
00:36:02,328 --> 00:36:03,448
If you don't shape up now,

588
00:36:03,567 --> 00:36:05,127
your business will collapse.

589
00:36:09,368 --> 00:36:10,408
Sorry, Miss Nie.

590
00:36:10,968 --> 00:36:11,567
If you...

591
00:36:11,567 --> 00:36:13,527
If you need those 20 portions urgently,

592
00:36:13,728 --> 00:36:15,687
I'll have to use frozen meat
from the freezer.

593
00:36:15,968 --> 00:36:17,607
It's fine. Take it easy, Mr. Changxi.

594
00:36:18,848 --> 00:36:20,487
The one supplying me

595
00:36:20,808 --> 00:36:23,248
is relying on his family's
pastures and cattle

596
00:36:23,248 --> 00:36:24,687
with quality meat,

597
00:36:24,848 --> 00:36:27,047
never fulfills his work properly,

598
00:36:27,808 --> 00:36:29,487
just like his dad,

599
00:36:29,728 --> 00:36:31,328
being a good-for-nothing drunkard.

600
00:36:32,607 --> 00:36:34,808
Genetics are interesting.

601
00:36:35,368 --> 00:36:36,167
Look at Tuo,

602
00:36:36,928 --> 00:36:37,968
a fine young man.

603
00:36:38,408 --> 00:36:40,007
Back when his dad worked at our mine,

604
00:36:40,047 --> 00:36:40,687
he was...

605
00:36:40,687 --> 00:36:41,368
Mr. Changxi.

606
00:36:43,087 --> 00:36:44,888
Why don't you go rest?

607
00:36:44,888 --> 00:36:46,328
We'll finish wrapping these.

608
00:36:48,288 --> 00:36:49,007
Right.

609
00:36:49,368 --> 00:36:50,527
Miss Nie needs to recuperate.

610
00:36:50,848 --> 00:36:51,448
Well,

611
00:36:51,448 --> 00:36:52,768
don't stay up too late.

612
00:36:52,968 --> 00:36:53,848
Got it.

613
00:36:54,127 --> 00:36:54,968
Rest up, Mr. Changxi.

614
00:37:00,768 --> 00:37:01,808
Blood bag?

615
00:37:07,368 --> 00:37:09,087
The blood bags Lin Xirou mentioned

616
00:37:10,207 --> 00:37:12,207
are humans with blood ties.

617
00:37:13,928 --> 00:37:14,968
Roommates

618
00:37:16,607 --> 00:37:18,647
are essentially reared as blood bags.

619
00:37:19,567 --> 00:37:20,928
Though they can't eat humans,

620
00:37:21,368 --> 00:37:23,087
blood bags are crucial to them.

621
00:37:23,248 --> 00:37:24,928
So, she has to ensure
their reproduction.

622
00:37:27,207 --> 00:37:28,487
(Xu Anni)
Humans with blood ties.

623
00:37:31,768 --> 00:37:32,848
How's the preparation?

624
00:37:33,487 --> 00:37:35,328
After pre-treatment,
we can remove the roots.

625
00:37:38,928 --> 00:37:39,768
Where's Xu Anni?

626
00:37:40,768 --> 00:37:41,808
Someone has taken over.

627
00:37:46,207 --> 00:37:48,167
Chen Fu's roommate is Xu Anni.

628
00:37:49,888 --> 00:37:52,047
Lin Ling and I met her dad as children.

629
00:37:54,328 --> 00:37:55,448
She has blood ties,

630
00:37:56,928 --> 00:37:58,408
and gets reared by Earth Fiends.

631
00:37:58,768 --> 00:37:59,928
Just like you said.

632
00:38:08,207 --> 00:38:09,448
Even if we know about it,

633
00:38:11,167 --> 00:38:12,687
where do we even start?

634
00:38:27,007 --> 00:38:27,808
Tell me,

635
00:38:28,368 --> 00:38:30,487
did we make progress today,

636
00:38:30,728 --> 00:38:32,047
or fall into another confusion?

637
00:38:35,888 --> 00:38:36,728
Regardless,

638
00:38:37,087 --> 00:38:39,487
Mr. Changxi made
great progress in his dumplings.

639
00:38:42,448 --> 00:38:43,207
Agreed.

640
00:38:45,448 --> 00:38:46,567
Mr. Changxi's dumplings

641
00:38:46,567 --> 00:38:47,888
not only nourish the body,

642
00:38:47,888 --> 00:38:49,127
but also sharpen the mind.

643
00:38:51,007 --> 00:38:53,087
Not inferior over Roadsound's medicine.

644
00:38:57,087 --> 00:38:57,728
Perfect timing.

645
00:38:57,888 --> 00:38:59,007
You should take antibiotics.

646
00:39:00,328 --> 00:39:01,487
Focus on recovering.

647
00:39:01,888 --> 00:39:02,687
We still have time.

648
00:39:17,647 --> 00:39:19,487
Rough day today.

649
00:39:21,248 --> 00:39:22,527
Is it rough?

650
00:39:22,968 --> 00:39:24,248
I'm just getting warmed up.

651
00:39:25,087 --> 00:39:26,728
If you want to go anywhere to have fun,

652
00:39:26,728 --> 00:39:27,687
just call me.

653
00:39:28,047 --> 00:39:29,448
I'd accept

654
00:39:29,448 --> 00:39:30,567
without hesitation.

655
00:39:36,047 --> 00:39:36,848
Lin Ling.

656
00:39:39,248 --> 00:39:40,408
This date with you

657
00:39:41,368 --> 00:39:42,527
was arranged by Ms. Lin.

658
00:39:43,328 --> 00:39:45,248
But befriending you

659
00:39:45,928 --> 00:39:46,687
is what I want.

660
00:39:52,487 --> 00:39:53,047
Here.

661
00:39:53,607 --> 00:39:54,487
Qingtuan rice balls.

662
00:41:19,200 --> 00:41:21,240
Today's weather is quite poetic.

663
00:41:21,840 --> 00:41:22,340
Right?

664
00:41:23,680 --> 00:41:25,600
The rain saturates the street
with tender grace.

665
00:41:26,240 --> 00:41:28,920
Green shades afar
are seen-yet-unseen in place.

666
00:41:34,000 --> 00:41:35,160
Am I annoying?

667
00:41:42,960 --> 00:41:44,240
Two yogurts, please.

668
00:41:48,520 --> 00:41:49,360
Perfect.

669
00:41:50,600 --> 00:41:53,240
Frozen-solid yogurts are the best.

670
00:41:54,560 --> 00:41:56,960
Just buy popsicles then.

671
00:42:02,040 --> 00:42:03,160
You take a non-frozen one.

672
00:42:04,240 --> 00:42:05,160
Cold foods are harmful.

673
00:42:05,600 --> 00:42:06,600
Especially for you girls,

674
00:42:06,800 --> 00:42:08,000
eat less cold foods.

675
00:42:08,880 --> 00:42:09,760
And,

676
00:42:10,840 --> 00:42:12,000
chill rises from the ground.

677
00:42:13,320 --> 00:42:14,480
Bare arms are fine,

678
00:42:14,840 --> 00:42:16,000
but keep legs covered.

679
00:42:17,520 --> 00:42:18,120
Put it on.

680
00:42:20,920 --> 00:42:21,760
Thanks.

681
00:42:23,600 --> 00:42:24,800
Health matters at any age.

682
00:42:25,480 --> 00:42:26,520
You don't care about it,

683
00:42:26,520 --> 00:42:28,000
but joint pains await later.

684
00:42:28,560 --> 00:42:29,280
Right?

685
00:42:30,800 --> 00:42:31,800
My jacket is nice.

686
00:42:33,000 --> 00:42:33,920
It's in lucky purple.

687
00:42:56,016 --> 00:43:00,376
♪The shapeless fire
clings to matter to illuminate♪

688
00:43:00,376 --> 00:43:04,696
♪Yet malice in darkness
defies the flame's pursuit♪

689
00:43:04,696 --> 00:43:09,136
♪A noble name must do righteous deeds♪

690
00:43:09,136 --> 00:43:11,576
♪After sunrise,
even wise words falter in truth♪

691
00:43:11,576 --> 00:43:15,656
♪Heaven-forged fire
scorches flesh and bone♪

692
00:43:15,656 --> 00:43:20,016
♪Dig out the truth buried
beneath the earth♪

693
00:43:20,016 --> 00:43:24,376
♪Heaven-sent tides can't
quench this reckless fire♪

694
00:43:24,376 --> 00:43:28,736
♪If we don't retreat,
we'll go through it together♪

695
00:43:28,736 --> 00:43:33,096
♪Heaven-kindled flames are different♪

696
00:43:33,096 --> 00:43:37,376
♪Truth's madness is hiding
under the surface♪

697
00:43:37,376 --> 00:43:41,936
♪The large waves are rolling
towards the sky♪

698
00:43:41,936 --> 00:43:49,656
♪Farewell to the old times,
and scenes fade away one by one♪

